snippet.title: Live Coding: Django AllAuth Package (OAuth2)
snippet.description:
Let's learn how to use the allauth package for Django! This package supports local registration and authentication, email verification, and integration with 3rd party login providers like Google, Facebook, GitHub, Discord, etc..
